What is redis ?

Redis is open source in memory  data structure store which can be used as a database and message broker 
No SQL / Key value store 
Supports multiple database structures
Built in replication

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Redis data types 

* string
* lists
* Sets 
* Sorted sets 
* Hashes 
* Bitmaps
* Hyperlogs
* Geospatial indexes

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
